headline: Nasdaq CFO Sarah Youngwood to Present at the Goldman Sachs U.S. Financial Services Conference
summary: NEW YORK, Dec. 05, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Nasdaq (Nasdaq: NDAQ) will be presenting at the following conference, with a webcast available at Nasdaq’s Investor Relations website: ir.nasdaq.com/events.cfm. Who:Sarah Youngwood, Executive Vice President & CFO, Nasdaq What:Goldman Sachs U.S. Financial Services Conference When:Wednesday, December 11, 2024 3:00 PM ET Where:Ms. Youngwood’s presentation will be webcast on Nasdaq’s Investor Relations website: ir.nasdaq.com/events.cfm. About Nasdaq Nasdaq
